OR ADVERSE EVENT HAS OCCURRED SINCE DECEMBER 31, 2008, THAT WOULD CAUSE A SIGNIFICANT CHANGE IN THE ESTIMATED PROVED RESERVES AS OF THAT DATE. FOR INFORMATION ON THE STANDARDIZED MEASURE OF DISCOUNTED FUTURE NET CASH FLOWS RELATING TO PROVED OIL AND

