THE BLOCKS FOURTH MAJOR DEVELOPMENT, KIZOMBA C, BEGAN PRODUCTION FROM THE MONDO AND SAXI/BATUQUE FIELDS IN 2008. A BLOCK-WIDE 3D AND 4D SEISMIC ACQUISITION PROGRAM CONCLUDED DURING THE YEAR. ON THE NON-OPERATED BLOCK 17, PROJECT WORK CONTINUED

ON THE PAZFLOR PROJECT IN 2008 AND DEVELOPMENT DRILLING CONTINUED AT ROSA AND DALIA. THE PLUTAO-SATURNO-VENUS-MARTE (PSVM) PROJECT ON BLOCK 31 (NON-OPERATED) WAS APPROVED IN 2008.

