RUSSIA

EXXONMOBILS NET ACREAGE HOLDINGS AT YEAR-END 2008 WERE 0.1 MILLION ACRES, ALL OFFSHORE. A TOTAL OF 2.7 NET DEVELOPMENT WELLS WERE COMPLETED IN

