THE CORPORATION CLASSIFIES INTEREST ON INCOME TAX-RELATED BALANCES AS INTEREST EXPENSE OR INTEREST

INCOME AND CLASSIFIES TAX-RELATED PENALTIES AS OPERATING EXPENSE.

