INTEREST EXPENSE ON INCOME TAX RESERVES IN 2008 AND 2007, RESPECTIVELY, AND HAD A RELATED INTEREST PAYABLE OF $671 MILLION AND $597 MILLION AT DECEMBER 31, 2008, AND 2007, RESPECTIVELY.

